  &lt;figcaption&gt;
    Let Unity generate the lightmap UVs for us.
  &lt;/figcaption&gt;


&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&#34;material-and-reflections&#34;&gt;Material and Reflections&lt;/h2&gt;
